   "source": [
    "Conclusion:\n",
    "p-value is small enought to reject the null hypothesis, which indicates a significant difference in number of calls between races. But my analysis above just focused on the relationship between race and call. As indicated from the table, there're more factors that could also contribute to the difference, e.g. gender.\n",
    "For amending the process to get the most important factor among all the others, it's neccessary to run above hypothesis on other factors and then compare the influence of all factors.\n"
